    <item>
      <title>前日本央行行长马赛表示，日本央行可能在年底前将利率提高至 0.5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/boj-may-hike-rate-to-0-5-by-year-end-ex-boj-s-masai-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行政策委员会前成员表示，如果经济状况大致保持在同一轨道上，日本央行有空间在今年年底前将基准利率上调至高达 0.5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/boj-may-hike-rate-to-0-5-by-year-end-ex-boj-s-masai-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 00:39:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
