    <item>
      <title>中国以接近创纪录的产量抵抗全球铜挤压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/china-defies-global-copper-squeeze-with-near-record-production</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球铜市场笼罩在对短缺的担忧之中，这已将价格推至创纪录水平，并引发了价值 490 亿美元的收购战。但在中国这个全球最大的精炼金属生产国和消费国，其供应量绰绰有余。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/china-defies-global-copper-squeeze-with-near-record-production</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 00:25:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
